# 14-37Guess Who: My Child Will Always Be My Child (Eng Sub)
26 @ # 20line # My Child Will Always Be My Child | 21:00 YT | Deven, a talented and passionate 26-year-old marketing planner for a travel agency, leads a seemingly ordinary life. But beneath the surface, he is a beacon of courage, hosting a podcast where he fearlessly discusses transgender issues. Despite the challenges, he boldly embarked on a journey three years ago by undergoing hormone replacement therapy, transitioning from female to male. In this episode, we follow Deven's journey as he navigates societal prejudices, inspires others, and embraces his true self. How did Deven's family react when he dropped the transgender bombshell? What surprising practical benefits have testosterone injections brought to Deven's life? Has Deven's transition had any effect on his love life? Let's find out! # # #Podcast #Podcaster # # # # # #
